sentence: how many rivers are in the state with the highest point ?
sentence-with-vars: how many rivers are in the state with the highest point ?
sql: select count ( river.river_name ) from river , highlow where river.traverse = highlow.state_name and highlow.highest_elevation = ( select max ( highlow.highest_elevation ) from highlow ) ;
